<h2 id="70">4. Activating the payment method</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Set up and activate the Payolution <a href="/en/payment/managing-payment-methods#20">payment method</a> in the <strong>Settings</strong> tab of the payment method. In addition, check the settings for <strong>Permitted payment methods</strong> in the <a href="/en/payment/managing-payment-methods#30">customer classes</a> and for <strong>Blocked payment methods</strong> in the <a href="/en/fulfilment/preparing-the-shipment#1000">shipping profiles</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
