<h2 id="90">6. Automatically sending shipping confirmations</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Set up an <a href="/en/automation/event-procedures">event procedure</a> to automatically send shipping confirmations to Payolution when the outgoing items are booked. You do not need a shipping confirmation for instalment purchases. As such, this event procedure should only be set up for payment on invoice.</p>
</div>
<div class="openblock collapseBox">
<div class="title">Setting up an event procedure</div>
<div class="content">
<div class="olist arabic">
